1929年，'''[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]'''在[[墨爾本|墨爾本]]進行了首次電視實驗播出<ref>''Australian TV – The First 25 Years'' by Peter Bielby, page 173. ISBN 0-17-005998-7</ref><ref>[http://www.environment.gov.au/heritage/ahc/publications/commission/books/linking-a-nation/chapter-9.html Linking a Nation] {{Wayback|url=http://www.environment.gov.au/heritage/ahc/publications/commission/books/linking-a-nation/chapter-9.html |date=20130405040444 }} – Chap 9 – Australian Heritage Council</ref><ref>Peter Luck, 50 Years of Australian Television ISBN 1-74110-367-3 p.15</ref>。之後澳大利亞在全國其他地方也進行了電視實驗播出，如1934年在[[布里斯班|布里斯班]]。1956年，澳大利亞的第一個電視台在[[雪梨_(城市)|雪梨]]開始播出<ref name="50Years">{{cite news| title = Australia celebrates 50 years of television| publisher = [[News_Limited|News Limited]]| url = http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/story/0,23663,20357015-5007183,00.html| date = 5 September 2006| accessdate = 1 August 2007| first = Erin| last = McWhirter| archive-date = 2008-03-11| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080311030441/http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/story/0,23663,20357015-5007183,00.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Ready, Set, Go to Digital – A Digital Action Plan for Australia |publisher=[[Department_of_Communications,_Information_Technology_and_the_Arts_(Australia)|DCITA]] |date=23 November 2008 |url=http://www.minister.dcita.gov.au/media/media_releases/ready,_set,_go_to_digital__a_digital_action_plan_for_australia |accessdate=19 August 2007 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070905071333/http://www.minister.dcita.gov.au/media/media_releases/ready,_set,_go_to_digital__a_digital_action_plan_for_australia |archivedate=2007年9月5日 }}</ref>。澳大利亞電視業的主要監管機構是澳大利亞通訊和媒體管理局。現在澳大利亞擁有兩家公共電視台[[ABC_(澳大利亞電視頻道)|ABC]]和[[特别广播服务公司|SBS]]，此外還有七號電視網、九號電視網、十號電視網等多家民營電視台。
